#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: payjp-for-wc.php
msgid "PAY.JP for WooCommerce"
msgstr "PAY.JP for WooCommerce"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: payjp-for-wc.php
msgid "https://wordpress.org/plugins/payjp-for-wc/"
msgstr ""

#. Description of the plugin
#: payjp-for-wc.php
msgid ""
"PAY.JP v2 payment gateway for WooCommerce. Supports credit card and PayPay "
"payments via Payment Widgets."
msgstr ""
"WooCommerce 向け PAY.JP v2 決済ゲートウェイ。Payment Widgets を使用したクレ"
"ジットカード・PayPay 決済に対応しています。"

#. Author of the plugin
#: payjp-for-wc.php
msgid "Shohei Tanaka"
msgstr ""

#. Author URI of the plugin
#: payjp-for-wc.php
msgid "https://artws.info"
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:49
msgid "PAY.JP"
msgstr "PAY.JP"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:73
msgid "API Settings"
msgstr "API 設定"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:82
msgid "Test Secret Key"
msgstr "テスト秘密鍵"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:88
msgid ""
"Found on the API keys page of your PAY.JP dashboard (test). Starts with "
"<code>sk_test_</code>. Keep this key secret and never expose it publicly."
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP ダッシュボード（テスト環境）の API キーページで確認できます。"
"<code>sk_test_</code> から始まる文字列です。外部に漏らさないよう厳重に管理し"
"てください。"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:91
msgid "Test Public Key"
msgstr "テスト公開鍵"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:97
msgid ""
"Found on the API keys page of your PAY.JP dashboard (test). Starts with "
"<code>pk_test_</code>."
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP ダッシュボード（テスト環境）の API キーページで確認できます。"
"<code>pk_test_</code> から始まる文字列です。"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:100
msgid "Live Secret Key"
msgstr "本番秘密鍵"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:106
msgid ""
"Found on the API keys page of your PAY.JP dashboard (live). Starts with "
"<code>sk_live_</code>. Keep this key secret and never expose it publicly."
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP ダッシュボード（本番環境）の API キーページで確認できます。"
"<code>sk_live_</code> から始まる文字列です。外部に漏らさないよう厳重に管理し"
"てください。"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:109
msgid "Live Public Key"
msgstr "本番公開鍵"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:115
msgid ""
"Found on the API keys page of your PAY.JP dashboard (live). Starts with "
"<code>pk_live_</code>."
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP ダッシュボード（本番環境）の API キーページで確認できます。"
"<code>pk_live_</code> から始まる文字列です。"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:118
msgid "Webhook Secret"
msgstr "Webhook シークレット"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:123
msgid ""
"The authentication token configured in PAY.JP Dashboard &gt; Webhooks. "
"Required for receiving payment and refund events on your server. Without "
"this, automatic order status updates via webhook will not work."
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP ダッシュボード &gt; Webhook で設定した認証トークンです。決済完了・返金"
"などのイベントをサーバーへ通知するために必要です。設定しない場合、Webhook に"
"よるオーダーステータスの自動更新が機能しません。"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:126
msgid "Test Mode"
msgstr "テストモード"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:131
msgid ""
"When enabled, test API keys are used and no real payments are processed. "
"Uncheck this and use live API keys for production."
msgstr ""
"チェックを入れると、テスト用 API キーで動作し実際の決済は発生しません。本番運"
"用時はチェックを外して本番用 API キーを使用してください。"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:143
msgid "Payment Methods"
msgstr "決済手段"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:157
msgid "Notifications"
msgstr "通知"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:162
msgid "Alert Email Address"
msgstr "異常通知メールアドレス"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:168
msgid ""
"Receives alerts when a payment anomaly is detected, such as a PAY.JP payment "
"confirmed for an already-cancelled order. Leave blank to use the site "
"administrator email address."
msgstr ""
"キャンセル済みの注文に対して PAY.JP の決済確定が検知されるなど、決済の異常が"
"発生した際に通知メールを受け取ります。空欄の場合はサイト管理者のメールアドレ"
"スが使用されます。"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:176
msgid "Debug"
msgstr "デバッグ"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:179
msgid ""
"Useful for diagnosing payment issues during development. Do not leave "
"enabled in production."
msgstr ""
"決済処理の問題調査や開発時に役立つオプションです。本番環境での常時有効化は避"
"けてください。"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:182
msgid "Debug Log"
msgstr "デバッグログ"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:186
msgid "Enable logging"
msgstr "ロギングを有効にする"

#. translators: 1: Opening <a> tag linking to WooCommerce log viewer, 2: Closing </a> tag
#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:190
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Logs PAY.JP API requests, responses, payment events, and received webhooks. "
"Enable only when debugging; keep off in production. Logs are available at "
"%1$sWooCommerce &gt; Status &gt; Logs%2$s."
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP API へのリクエスト・レスポンス・決済イベント・Webhook の受信内容をログ"
"ファイルに記録します。問題の調査やデバッグ時のみ有効にし、本番環境では通常は"
"オフにしてください。ログは %1$sWooCommerce &gt; ステータス &gt; ログ%2$s で確"
"認できます。"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:201
msgid "Webhook"
msgstr "Webhook"

#. translators: %s: URL to PAY.JP test mode documentation
#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:282
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Test mode is active. <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener "
"noreferrer\">View test card numbers and test accounts &rarr;</a>"
msgstr ""
"テストモードが有効です。<a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener "
"noreferrer\">テストカード番号とテストアカウントを確認する &rarr;</a>"

#. translators: %s: URL to PAY.JP PayPay test documentation
#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:295
#, php-format
msgid ""
"PayPay is enabled. <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener "
"noreferrer\">View PayPay test accounts and instructions &rarr;</a>"
msgstr ""
"PayPay が有効です。<a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener "
"noreferrer\">PayPay テストアカウントと手順を確認する &rarr;</a>"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:320
msgid "Open PAY.JP Dashboard"
msgstr "PAY.JP ダッシュボードを開く"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:321
msgid "Manage API keys, webhooks, and payments on the PAY.JP Dashboard."
msgstr "PAY.JP ダッシュボードで API キー・Webhook・決済を管理できます。"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:325
msgid "Create a PAY.JP Account"
msgstr "PAY.JP アカウントを作成する"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:326
msgid "You need a PAY.JP account to accept payments. Sign up for free."
msgstr "決済を受け付けるには PAY.JP アカウントが必要です。無料で登録できます。"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:357
#: src/blocks/checkout/payment-method-card.js:23
msgid "Credit Card (PAY.JP)"
msgstr "クレジットカード（PAY.JP）"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:358
#: src/blocks/checkout/payment-method-paypay.js:13
msgid "PayPay (PAY.JP)"
msgstr "PayPay（PAY.JP）"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:362
msgid "Payment Method"
msgstr "決済手段"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:366
msgid "Enable Payment Methods"
msgstr "有効にする決済手段"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:381
msgid ""
"Checked payment methods will appear on the checkout page. API keys must also "
"be configured for them to be available."
msgstr ""
"チェックを入れた決済手段がチェックアウト画面に表示されます。表示するには API "
"キーの設定も必要です。"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:400
msgid "Webhook URL"
msgstr "Webhook URL"

#. translators: 1: Opening <strong> tag, 2: Closing </strong> tag
#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:416
#, php-format
msgid "Register the URL above in %1$sPAY.JP Dashboard &gt; Webhooks%2$s."
msgstr ""
"上記の URL を %1$sPAY.JP ダッシュボード &gt; Webhooks%2$s に登録してくださ"
"い。"

#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:423
msgid "Enable the following events:"
msgstr "以下のイベントを有効にしてください："

#. translators: 1: Opening <strong> tag, 2: Closing </strong> tag
#: includes/admin/class-payjp-admin-settings-page.php:435
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Set the %1$sWebhook Secret%2$s from PAY.JP Dashboard into the \"Webhook "
"Secret\" field above and save."
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP ダッシュボードの %1$sWebhook Secret%2$s を上の「Webhook シークレット」"
"フィールドに入力して保存してください。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-api.php:143
msgid "PAY.JP returned an unexpected non-JSON response."
msgstr "PAY.JP から予期しない非 JSON レスポンスが返されました。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-api.php:152
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-api.php:174
msgid "An unknown PAY.JP error occurred."
msgstr "PAY.JP で不明なエラーが発生しました。"

#. translators: %d: HTTP status code
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-api.php:183
#, php-format
msgid "PAY.JP API returned HTTP %d."
msgstr "PAY.JP API が HTTP %d を返しました。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-pending-payment-monitor.php:191
msgid "PAY.JP: Payment confirmed via status polling."
msgstr "PAY.JP: ステータスポーリングにより決済が確認されました。"

#. translators: PAY.JP order note shown in WooCommerce admin for manual-capture orders confirmed via status polling.
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-pending-payment-monitor.php:210
msgid ""
"PAY.JP authorised via status polling. Payment will be captured when the "
"order is marked Completed."
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP ステータスポーリングによりオーソリが確認されました。注文を「完了」に変"
"更するとキャプチャが実行されます。"

#. translators: %s: PAY.JP Payment Flow status (e.g. "payment_failed").
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-pending-payment-monitor.php:229
#, php-format
msgid ""
"PAY.JP payment did not complete (status: %s, detected via status polling)."
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP 決済が完了しませんでした（ステータス: %s、ステータスポーリングで検"
"出）。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-pending-payment-monitor.php:294
msgid ""
"PAY.JP: Payment could not be confirmed by status polling. The order is again "
"subject to the standard automatic cancellation of unpaid orders."
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP: ステータスポーリングで決済を確認できませんでした。この注文は通常の未"
"払い注文の自動キャンセルの対象に戻ります。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-subscriptions.php:87
msgid "PAY.JP: No subscription found for this renewal order."
msgstr "PAY.JP: この更新注文に対するサブスクリプションが見つかりません。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-subscriptions.php:100
msgid ""
"PAY.JP: No saved payment method found for this subscription. Please update "
"the payment method."
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP: このサブスクリプションに保存済みの支払い方法が見つかりません。支払い"
"方法を更新してください。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-subscriptions.php:144
msgid "PAY.JP: Renewal payment failed or requires additional authentication."
msgstr "PAY.JP: 更新支払いが失敗したか、追加認証が必要です。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-token-manager.php:81
msgid "Failed to create PAY.JP customer."
msgstr "PAY.JP 顧客の作成に失敗しました。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-token-manager.php:106
msgid "Failed to create card setup session."
msgstr "カードセットアップセッションの作成に失敗しました。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-token-manager.php:143
msgid "Invalid card setup session."
msgstr "無効なカードセットアップセッションです。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-token-manager.php:165
msgid "Card setup was not completed. Please try again."
msgstr "カードの設定が完了しませんでした。もう一度お試しください。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-token-manager.php:175
msgid "Card setup completed but no payment method was returned."
msgstr "カードの設定は完了しましたが、支払い方法が返されませんでした。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-token-manager.php:190
msgid "Card saved successfully."
msgstr "カードを保存しました。"

#. translators: 1: PAY.JP PaymentMethod ID, 2: error message
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-token-manager.php:365
#, php-format
msgid "PAY.JP: Failed to save card %1$s after payment: %2$s"
msgstr "PAY.JP: 支払い後にカード %1$s の保存に失敗しました: %2$s"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:193
msgid "PAY.JP: Payment confirmed via webhook."
msgstr "PAY.JP: Webhook経由で決済が確認されました。"

#. translators: 1: WooCommerce order status the order already had (e.g. "cancelled"), 2: PAY.JP Payment Flow ID.
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:236
#, php-format
msgid ""
"PAY.JP: Payment was confirmed for this order after it was already %1$s. The "
"payment is captured on PAY.JP but is NOT reflected on this order. Review the "
"PAY.JP dashboard and either refund the payment or handle the order manually. "
"(Payment Flow ID: %2$s)"
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP: この注文が既に %1$s になった後で決済確定が確認されました。PAY.JP 側で"
"は決済が完了していますが、この注文には反映されていません。PAY.JP ダッシュボー"
"ドを確認のうえ、返金するか注文を手動で処理してください。（Payment Flow ID: "
"%2$s）"

#. translators: %s: WooCommerce order number.
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:245
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:415
#, php-format
msgid "Order: #%s"
msgstr "注文: #%s"

#. translators: %s: WooCommerce order status (e.g. "cancelled").
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:250
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:420
#, php-format
msgid "Current order status: %s"
msgstr "現在の注文ステータス: %s"

#. translators: %s: PAY.JP Payment Flow ID.
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:255
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:425
#, php-format
msgid "Payment Flow ID: %s"
msgstr "Payment Flow ID: %s"

#. translators: %s: Payment amount in JPY, formatted with thousands separators.
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:262
#, php-format
msgid "Amount: ¥%s"
msgstr "金額: ¥%s"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:266
msgid ""
"Review the payment on the PAY.JP dashboard and either refund it or handle "
"the order manually."
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP ダッシュボードで該当の決済を確認のうえ、返金するか注文を手動で処理して"
"ください。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:270
msgid "PAY.JP payment confirmed for a closed order — action required"
msgstr "PAY.JP: 確定済み注文への決済確認 — 対応が必要です"

#. translators: PAY.JP order note shown in WooCommerce admin for manual-capture orders confirmed via webhook.
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:313
msgid ""
"PAY.JP authorised via webhook. Payment will be captured when the order is "
"marked Completed."
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP Webhook経由でオーソリが完了しました。注文を「完了」に変更するとキャプ"
"チャが実行されます。"

#. translators: 1: WooCommerce order status the order already had (e.g. "cancelled"), 2: PAY.JP Payment Flow ID.
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:379
#, php-format
msgid ""
"PAY.JP: A PayPay authorization completed for this order after it was already "
"%1$s. The authorization has been automatically voided. (Payment Flow ID: "
"%2$s)"
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP: この注文が既に %1$s になった後で PayPay のオーソリが完了しました。"
"オーソリは自動的に取り消されました。（Payment Flow ID: %2$s）"

#. translators: 1: WooCommerce order status the order already had (e.g. "cancelled"), 2: PAY.JP Payment Flow ID.
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:388
#, php-format
msgid ""
"PAY.JP: A PayPay authorization completed for this order after it was already "
"%1$s. Automatic void FAILED — the customer's funds remain reserved. Cancel "
"the payment on the PAY.JP dashboard. (Payment Flow ID: %2$s)"
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP: この注文が既に %1$s になった後で PayPay のオーソリが完了しました。自"
"動取り消しに失敗しました — 顧客の与信枠は確保されたままです。PAY.JP ダッシュ"
"ボードで決済を取り消してください。（Payment Flow ID: %2$s）"

#. translators: 1: WooCommerce order status the order already had (e.g. "cancelled"), 2: PAY.JP Payment Flow ID.
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:397
#, php-format
msgid ""
"PAY.JP: A PayPay authorization completed for this order after it was already "
"%1$s. Automatic void was not attempted for this order — cancel the payment "
"manually on the PAY.JP dashboard if needed. (Payment Flow ID: %2$s)"
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP: この注文が既に %1$s になった後で PayPay のオーソリが完了しました。自"
"動取り消しは実行されませんでした — 必要に応じて PAY.JP ダッシュボードで決済を"
"手動で取り消してください。（Payment Flow ID: %2$s）"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:405
msgid "The uncaptured authorization has been automatically voided."
msgstr "未キャプチャのオーソリは自動的に取り消されました。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:407
msgid ""
"Automatic void FAILED — the customer's funds remain reserved. Cancel the "
"payment on the PAY.JP dashboard."
msgstr ""
"自動取り消しに失敗しました — 顧客の与信枠は確保されたままです。PAY.JP ダッ"
"シュボードで決済を取り消してください。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:409
msgid ""
"Automatic void was not attempted for this order. Cancel the payment manually "
"on the PAY.JP dashboard if needed."
msgstr ""
"この注文では自動取り消しは実行されませんでした。必要に応じて PAY.JP ダッシュ"
"ボードで決済を手動で取り消してください。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:433
msgid "PAY.JP authorization received for a closed order"
msgstr "PAY.JP: 確定済み注文へのオーソリ受信"

#. translators: PAY.JP failed payment note shown in WooCommerce admin
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:515
msgid "PAY.JP payment failed (webhook)."
msgstr "PAY.JP 決済が失敗しました（Webhook）。"

#. translators: 1: PAY.JP refund ID, 2: refund amount in JPY
#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-payjp-webhook-handler.php:560
#, php-format
msgid "PAY.JP refund created (webhook). Refund ID: %1$s. Amount: ¥%2$s."
msgstr "PAY.JP 返金が作成されました（Webhook）。返金 ID: %1$s。金額: ¥%2$s。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-wc-gateway-payjp-card.php:43
msgid "PAY.JP Credit Card"
msgstr "PAY.JP クレジットカード"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-wc-gateway-payjp-card.php:44
msgid "Accept credit card payments via PAY.JP v2 Payment Widgets."
msgstr ""
"PAY.JP v2 Payment Widgets を使用したクレジットカード決済を受け付けます。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-wc-gateway-payjp-card.php:90
msgid ""
"After clicking \"Place order\", you will be taken to a secure page to enter "
"your card details."
msgstr ""
"「注文する」ボタンをクリックすると、カード情報を入力するセキュアなページに移"
"動します。"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-wc-gateway-payjp-card.php:95
msgid "Save payment methods"
msgstr "支払い方法を保存する"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-wc-gateway-payjp-card.php:97
msgid "Allow customers to save their card for future purchases"
msgstr "お客様が今後の購入のためにカードを保存できるようにする"

#: includes/gateways/payjp/class-wc-gateway-payjp-card.php:101
